t: "Ass ideg ara ten Ifser meĂŽĂŽa: \"a yagraw n leonun, ni$ tcerrĂąem deg imdanen\"? A d inin imawlan nnsen, seg imdanen: \"a Mass nne$! Kra segne$ $elten si kra, Nebbwev ar lajel nne$, i $ Terriv\". Inna: \"d times ay d tanezdu$t nnwen, ad degs twekkĂŽem, siwa ma ur aS ihwi i Ăebbi\". Ih, Mass ik d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab, d Amusnaw"